      "clean_path": "/mnt/d/Diary_agent/journals/cleaned/2026/04/2026-04-20--ab002fee-786e-434c-8877-4bc67519784b.md"
    },
    {
      "source_id": 51,
      "source_uuid": "9e130830-1243-40b7-b945-7809804d2877",
      "source_created_at": "2026-04-25T10:39:55.411414+08:00",
      "source_updated_at": "2026-04-25 10:39:55.411420",
      "source_topic": "人生",
      "source_category": "THOUGHT",
      "source_key": "project_pa:entries:51@2026-04-25T10:39:55.411414+08:00",
      "raw_sha256": "8c466d83aaae939aabc951dc216cb890d3bd5868f289e3f94eca7cc862099ea4",
      "entry_date": "2026-04-25",
      "target_entry_id": "f567548a-c9ac-4b92-b307-a8f46fbffc9d",
      "entry_type": "thought",
      "status": "confirmed",
      "clean_unchanged": true,
      "segments": [
        {
          "position": 0,
          "text": "我今天读到万维钢说德国一位社会学家Hartmut Rosa提到人生必须要有个Mission， 而找到Resonance是实现这个使命过程中非常重要的陪伴，让你不再孤单，也让你保持活力。争取实现高使命，高共鸣的人生，把自己围绕在志同道合的人身边，才能更好地真正实现自我。",
          "theme": "人生目标与价值观",
          "tags": [
            "个人与家庭成长"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "uncertainties": [],
      "links": [],
      "followups": [],
      "original_path": "/mnt/d/Diary_agent/journals/originals/2026/04/2026-04-25--f567548a-c9ac-4b92-b307-a8f46fbffc9d.md",
      "clean_path": "/mnt/d/Diary_agent/journals/cleaned/2026/04/2026-04-25--f567548a-c9ac-4b92-b307-a8f46fbffc9d.md"
    },
    {
      "source_id": 65,
      "source_uuid": "e251b895-2b61-46cb-956f-ed3bad00a1e5",
      "source_created_at": "2026-05-06T23:39:20.433338+08:00",
      "source_updated_at": "2026-05-06 23:39:20.433408",
      "source_topic": "思维",
      "source_category": "THOUGHT",
      "source_key": "project_pa:entries:65@2026-05-06T23:39:20.433338+08:00",
      "raw_sha256": "24b39b05cf3b1282ffb9f943c623e5e149235cdedb61628252600467bd3be996",
      "entry_date": "2026-05-06",
      "target_entry_id": "0a7830c9-6cc1-4c11-b66a-e0154de5de55",
      "entry_type": "thought",
      "status": "confirmed",
      "clean_unchanged": true,
      "segments": [
        {
          "position": 0,
          "text": "人的智商本身不是重点，因为人脑子的智商就像模型的版本一样，可能有些人用很厉害的模型，有些人用很一般的模型，但是真正拉开差距的是你怎么用它，就是你的harness，你的思维模式，你的行为习惯等等，才是决定你能不能完全用出你智商的上限。这些Harness. 这些行为习惯、思维模式等等，是可以后天学习的，也是可以传授的，这才是人应该努力的主要方向",
          "theme": "人生目标与价值观",
          "tags": [
